        <item>
            <title>1.7.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 20:51:33 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>17</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.7.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.7.0</h2>
<p>Otto now handles school and money together: keep your class schedule next to your Costco shifts (with clash warnings), track assignments and paste in a syllabus, get quizzed from your own notes, see whether your next paycheck covers the bills due before the one after, have wake-up calls follow your schedule, and get a heads-up when an autopay bill comes in unusually high.</p>
]]></description>
